Class Tuple

java.lang.Object
de.gnwi.mfsim.model.peptide.utils.configuration.Tuple
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Point
public class Tuple extends Object implements Serializable
A class representing the abstract mathematical entity "n dimenssional Tuple". Data format is double.

Ziv Yaniv

      public boolean equals(Tuple t, double epsilon)

      Parameters:

      epsilon - The L infinity norm of the difference between tuples is compared to this value.
